{"tid":1176014,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞主席堅稱華維迪屹立不倒","createTime":"2019-05-29T02:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T07:22:05.000Z","uid":186071,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"34053fc051381f261412b5af5620b72544505bd4","tid":1176014,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"【RAC1電台為誤報致歉，巴塞主席堅稱華維迪屹立不倒｜體嘢報道】<br />\n<br />\n閱讀全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p75t7v-6Oj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp75t7v-6Oj&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=e96ff1d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p75t7v-6Oj</a><br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿喉舌報章《每日體育報》（Mundo Deportivo）引述球會內部人士指，主教練華維迪（Ernesto Valverde）被炒只是誤傳消息。誤報華維迪被炒的RAC 1電台，主動為誤報消息道歉；Cardena Ser電台更主動聯絡巴塞主席巴杜武（Josep Maria Bartomeu），他確認華維迪不會被炒。<br />\n<br />\n#體嘢<br />\n=================<br />\n企高一格 全新體法<br />\n精彩深入評論，盡在體嘢 SportsYeah<br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sportsyeah/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsportsyeah%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=cf1afe43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sportsyeah/</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/sportsyeah\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsportsyeah&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=2d81172f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sportsyeah</a><br />\nWebsite: <a href=\"http://www.sportsyeah.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsyeah.hk&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=c5a7e4e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sportsyeah.hk</a><br />\n懂球帝帳號：SportsYeah / 香港體嘢"},{"pid":"8d9207f5a52ae4720af1a048220b79d2cfc8bf59","tid":1176014,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"仆街啦華維迪"},{"pid":"ac546ae318dee216ebd08d77c2fef21c24b4a261","tid":1176014